    "However, the DLM-DTI with knowledge adaptation exhibited weaknesses in generalization performance.",
    "Kang et al. 's [43] work also demonstrated strong performance under coldsplitting conditions (Table 8).",
    "In contrast, our DLM-DTI, which either matched or outperformed Kang et al.",
